{"tid":1955464,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"為左答謝同路手足支持黃店咁耐","createTime":"2020-04-02T13:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T08:46:10.000Z","uid":304230,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7eaf53de9dc4572bd4a6277a0ba2a411ca487718","tid":1955464,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:12:55.000Z","msg":"相信肺炎令到唔小店鋪陷入困境<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好慶幸我地仲捱得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我地之前買左消毒液 <br />\n<br />\n以成本價賣返出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢筆錢諗住用黎答謝大家咁耐既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約有$10000左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有需要我地可以另外再拎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗到幾個方案點用<br />\n<br />\n1. 租個地方以小班教學教大家整野飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    每班一小時教學 一對三?（怕死）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    可能一個禮拜三日 一日五個鐘?<br />\n    可以教到簡單mocktail/cocktail?<br />\n    因為我地整野飲都唔係好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    可以當係興趣班咁 不設收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.買口罩/消毒紙巾係鋪頭派?<br />\n   但係好似市面上都買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.如果有更好提議可以比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e279be4354c72cbd8f6cfc8fbf4162593ec8d05c","tid":1955464,"uid":92021,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你<br />\n好有錢呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捱過咗今次先好再諗呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20606859e91c999476a409af54cc576f66164311","tid":1955464,"uid":107717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"keep住筆錢應急先啦<br />\n武肺唔知last到幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93b75b2091ab004769785c4934627776d2e4e39","tid":1955464,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e279be4354c72cbd8f6cfc8fbf4162593ec8d05c","tid":1955464,"uid":92021,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你<br />\n好有錢呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捱過咗今次先好再諗呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"本身筆錢都係拎出黎支持大家<br />\n做人要有口齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024991bab391968658d5f6bc762827080971f2b5","tid":1955464,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20606859e91c999476a409af54cc576f66164311","tid":1955464,"uid":107717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"keep住筆錢應急先啦<br />\n武肺唔知last到幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:18:20.000Z","msg":"我都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係筆錢係應承左大家賣完會拎出黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271bb3a2ed5ad16f70d3c8ca8589375bf290021d","tid":1955464,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T13:20:26.000Z","msg":"教沖野飲我第一個參加！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58eec593d71a35a2eba8f0f3a6ca8cf60ea834c4","tid":1955464,"uid":92021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"024991bab391968658d5f6bc762827080971f2b5","tid":1955464,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20606859e91c999476a409af54cc576f66164311","tid":1955464,"uid":107717,"like":